---
description: Read project rules before making any code edit
alwaysApply: true
---
Before editing code in this project:
- Read `AGENTS.md`
- Read `.cursorrules`
- Read `AI-EDIT-PRECHECK.md`
- Identify the controlling file, data source, event trigger, style location, and clone-sensitive values.

When the request involves slug/category/path/routing/navigation:
- Check `page.meta.json`
- Check generated JSON (`shop/data/shop-catalog.json`, `data/site-map.json`)
- Check render logic in JS
- Check href/path/folder mapping
- Do not hardcode old slug values from cloned folders.
